  "intent": "Prepare a qPCR plate by distributing three different master mixes (22\u00b5L each) from tube rack positions A1, B1, and C1 to designated wells across the 96-well plate. Add 3\u00b5L spike DNA to wells A1-A2, then sequentially add 3\u00b5L of three different GCN DNA standards to wells A1-A2, A3-A4, and A5-A6 respectively. Add 3\u00b5L water to wells A7-A12 as no-template controls. Finally, transfer 3.5\u00b5L DNA samples from row A of the DNA plate to all corresponding rows of the qPCR plate using an 8-channel pipette, mixing twice after each transfer.",
